s/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a135e88f1e5cedf77b7e4d9b5a9fb18354db9475","tid":1115802,"uid":168698,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:33:32.000Z","msg":"無得救，班男仔，警察加校長伊斯蘭入腦太嚴重，<br />\n<br />\n最終介入都係小數上流人士，何妨上流想搞點件事可能為左息事寧人幫自己國家洗白，<br />\n<br />\n伊斯蘭太容易激發人既原始獸性，對於想犯罪既人來講伊斯蘭就係最好既理由"},{"pid":"9c4e90ba7d96af00953bc2e0929e89e060c450d7","tid":1115802,"uid":55375,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"你話個校長咁做好撚惡 但都叫做明佢諗咩<br />\n<br />\n幫佢個班學生到底諗咩？尤其係d女(罩袍=女)無端端就幫手殺咗佢 做乜鳩？"},{"pid":"2a9be92853ae9e84f4021bd026f9e4943c6954ef","tid":1115802,"uid":30578,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"連登:一定係著得少布引校長摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0c47cc47d4a3b2faeea96e985caec1ebdb5425","tid":1115802,"uid":81190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:47:07.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨仲唔係搵到個新地方去輸出革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就唔係剩只批鬥資本家，而係捉呢啲畜生去批鬥<br />\n支持中共解放印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec488b53b2a82fec050ec37e1c95ad3abc887add","tid":1115802,"uid":165336,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9c4e90ba7d96af00953bc2e0929e89e060c450d7","tid":1115802,"uid":55375,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"你話個校長咁做好撚惡 但都叫做明佢諗咩<br />\n<br />\n幫佢個班學生到底諗咩？尤其係d女(罩袍=女)無端端就幫手殺咗佢 做乜鳩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T14:13:04.000Z","msg":"文明世界既人係唔會明白生番既思維"},{"pid":"471cba279571ae32826d205567fa863c0d96a99e","tid":1115802,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T19:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96eba8f0cc5f67d96d27f56bd80c5ad4c247799f","tid":1115802,"uid":26773,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T19:51:38.000Z","msg":"民眾開始責備拉菲。<br />\n垃圾國家"},{"pid":"851e97194fada52c1f1b109b7c930e8aa4e0d7f9","tid":1115802,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce6ddc23fc6384fa1d0f199c5a1a1bf661fdc4d","tid":1115802,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}